name: Unsupervised
overview: Two 15-year-old best friends, Gary and Joel, they try to navigate through teenage life while also trying to do the right thing without the help of any parental supervision.

episodes.name: Pilot
episodes.overview: Gary and Joel realize they're looked at as kids, so they try to change their image to hook up with girls.

episodes.name: Rich Girl
episodes.overview: Gary and Joel realize that they're poor, so they try to set up Gary's stepmother with a rich guy who's the father of a new student at their school.

episodes.name: Field of Dreams ... and Dogs
episodes.overview: In an attempt to surround themselves with good influences, Gary and Joel decide to manage the high school baseball team.

episodes.name: Fires & Liars
episodes.overview: Gary and Joel “defend” the local fire department by becoming arsonists.

episodes.name: Stupid Idiots
episodes.overview: Gary and Joel discover that they’re in the slow track at school and stage a student uprising to abolish academic segregation.

episodes.name: Nits
episodes.overview: An outbreak of head lice threatens Gary and Joel’s plans to hook up with girls at a school dance.

episodes.name: The Magic of Science
episodes.overview: Gary and Joel enlist a psychic to help them win the science fair.

episodes.name: My Brother Brian
episodes.overview: Joel's 40-year-old brother, Brian, moves back into Joel's bedroom and Joel strives to be more tolerant of him despite Brian's contemptible behavior.

episodes.name: Jesse Judge Lawncare Incorporated
episodes.overview: Gary and Joel try and acquire sweet tans and mad paper by hooking up with a young lawncare entrepreneur.

episodes.name: Youngbloods
episodes.overview: Gary and Joel get fake ID's so they can give blood.

episodes.name: The Great Traveler's Road
episodes.overview: Gary and Joel learn the meaning of school pride when a turf war erupts with prep school kids over their prized food mart.

episodes.name: Black Squirrels
episodes.overview: When Joel's brother Brian gets out of prison, the boys get him a job as their High School head of security only to find out some people can never be reformed.

episodes.name: Reggie Dog Bites
episodes.overview: The boys discover the true ugliness of death after they save Carol's ex, Reggie, from being buried in an unmarked grave and get stuck disposing of his body themselves.
